      <lg xml:id="TolE0144">
<l>ñanama yavaveṉu mutalāku moḻiyu</l>
<l>muyirmuta lākiya moḻiyu muḷappaṭa</l>
<l>vaṉṟi yaṉaittu mellā vaḻiyu</l>
<l>niṉṟa coṉmu ṉiyalpā kummē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When the initial sound of the succeeding word is</l>
<l><foreign xml:lang="ta">ñ, n, m, y, v,</foreign> or when the initial sound is a vowel,</l>
<l>no change takes place,</l>
<l>whatever be the final sound of the standing word,</l>
<l>and whatever be its relationship.<note place="foot">E.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">viḷa|tāḻ ñaṉratu, nīṇṭatu, māṇtatu, yātu, valitu .... etc.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
